- @root: Return to main

@rb_attack
title: Confront fascist paramilitaries!
view-if: social_fascism_adopted = 0
subtitle: Buchwitz orders Reichsbanner units to engage hostile paramilitaries with streetfighting!
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0 and rb_strength >= 1000 and rb_militancy > 0.25 and strife >= 5
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 8; sh_strength -= sh_strength * 0.15; ss_strength -= ss_strength * 0.15; rb_strength -= rb_strength * 0.20; nationalism -= nationalism * 0.03; dnvp_relation -= 5; nsdap_relation -= 10; left_dissent += 2; pro_republic += 1; reichsbanner_timer -= 5; strife += 2; pacifism -= 2; workers_spd *= 0.99; new_middle_spd *= 0.97

Under Buchwitz's avant-garde, we engage with fascist paramilitaries! This has weakened both our and their paramilitaries.

@iron_front_mobilization
title: Reichsbanner's militarization.
view-if: social_fascism_adopted = 0
subtitle: Strengthen the Iron Front as a visible anti-fascist counterweight!
choose-if: iron_front_formed = 1 and advisor_action_timer <= 0
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; rb_strength += rb_strength * 0.01; rb_militancy += 0.04; workers_nsdap -= 2; workers_dnvp -= 1; sh_militancy += 0.02; ss_militancy += 0.02; nationalism -= nationalism * 0.02; z_relation -= 2; dvp_relation -= 2; reichsbanner_timer -= 3; strife += 1; pacifism -= 2

Seeing how unarmed our units are and easily intimidated by far right paramilitaries, we have begun giving away arms from both reserves of military and buying out old weapons.

@rb_expansion
title: Recruitment to the Reichsbanner.
subtitle: Systematic recruitment under Buchwitz’s direction!
view-if: social_fascism_adopted = 0
choose-if: advisor_action_timer <= 0
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 8; rb_strength += rb_strength * 0.08; rb_militancy += 0.01; workers_spd += 1; center_strength -= 0.5; reichsbanner_timer -= 4; pacifism -= 1

We expand the scope of recruitment towards the Reichsbanner, increasing membership count.

